{"tid":1644621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩證實左人一藍腦即殘","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:52:43.000Z","uid":264530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5cbda242c0c9ab6c8dee1d6f96245413ca3826","tid":1644621,"uid":264530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"我老豆從來都話自己係中立 不問世事 頭先佢無啦啦send D野比我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEqUHKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEqUHKj.jpg&h=ee439e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/mcadh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fmcadh&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5ZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=f462494a\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/mcadh</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔好再sendD咁嘅野比我全部假野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你做乜咁大脾氣 我轉發畀你睇咋嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你咁樣講即係認為我地係曱甴？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你哋收曬美國錢 出嚟搞亂香港 搞到我放工無車撘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我都想收錢 計翻200萬人出黎十幾次美國 晨早破產la 我都想收錢 錢呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你哋咪比人煽動嘅傻仔囉 週街打爛嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你知唔知721發生啲咩事 啲黑社會打人 <br />\nD狗三十幾分鐘都未到 mtr縱容佢哋做㗎 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我唔想知 我就負責揾錢 如果地下有把 機關槍 掃曬你地班冚家鏟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 你唔好講呢啲嘢呀 人哋打到你仆街 咁冇良心嘅嘢都講得出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 你咁惡做乜嘢 你以後唔使叫我唔會再養你  叫佢哋養你 講得冇錯 97美國佬排人黎搞亂香港 你哋仲打阿婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你畀打阿婆啲片畀我睇 我逐一同你解釋<br />\n<br />\n之後佢勁大力閂門入咗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔聽我講嘢<br />\n之前都叫佢唔好睇tvb、微信 全部都係中國嘢假嘅 捏造事實 跟住佢話保持政治中立 唔理呢啲嘢 咁我廢事幫佢手機down蘋果 因為佢成日返大陸 但係今日冇啦啦send啲咁嘅片畀我 證明咗人一藍腦即殘 廢事同佢解釋<br />\n<br />\nbtw  有冇人介紹啲工畀我 可以畀我交到學費同應付生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ee11b1f427d1a341f186ff42ab9993f1c4cfaf","tid":1644621,"uid":332797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"突發！美國人要大家教佢點抵制暴雪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca7f207de7047d788ffab2263b0831c8e3ea2ac6","tid":1644621,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"用返佢所講嘅嘢套落警甴到<br />\n班警甴打爛哂d野！<br />\n班警甴打呀婆！<br />\n班警甴收政府錢出黎搞事！受煽動！<br />\n示威者應該攞機關槍殺哂班警甴！"},{"pid":"24b263852872b8357152f1df768a6fd863c1ab5a","tid":1644621,"uid":264530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7f207de7047d788ffab2263b0831c8e3ea2ac6","tid":1644621,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"用返佢所講嘅嘢套落警甴到<br />\n班警甴打爛哂d野！<br />\n班警甴打呀婆！<br />\n班警甴收政府錢出黎搞事！受煽動！<br />\n示威者應該攞機關槍殺哂班警甴！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"我都想 佢都唔撚聽我講嘢成日睇tvb 一講就話唔理呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db31b6602bd5f353a581f11fb35396c1a5f88f65","tid":1644621,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24b263852872b8357152f1df768a6fd863c1ab5a","tid":1644621,"uid":264530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7f207de7047d788ffab2263b0831c8e3ea2ac6","tid":1644621,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"用返佢所講嘅嘢套落警甴到<br />\n班警甴打爛哂d野！<br />\n班警甴打呀婆！<br />\n班警甴收政府錢出黎搞事！受煽動！<br />\n示威者應該攞機關槍殺哂班警甴！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1